The Speaker of the House of Representatives, Femi Gbajabiamila, has congratulated Joe Ajaero on his emergence as the new president of the Nigeria Labour Congress. Gbajabiamila also congratulated other members of the new national executive committee of the NLC. In a press statement by his Special Adviser on Media and Publicity, Lanre Lasisi, the Speaker said he believed Ajaero would bring his experience to bear in his new position as the president of the NLC. Gbajabiamila wished Ajaero a successful tenure, urging the new NLC president to be innovative in his leadership.